at worked with infocards. So after much effort, I did find a &lt;a href=&quot;http://rapidshare.de/files/11577739/Internet.Explorer.7.Build.5299-JCXP.rar.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ie7 Build 5299 download on rapidshare&lt;/a&gt;. So in case you would like to use &lt;a href=&quot;http://bink.nu/Article5918.bink&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ie7 Build 5299&lt;/a&gt;, here are the download links.&lt;br/&gt;
